<?php $__env->startSection('content'); ?><p>Modern Family alum Ariel Winter flaunted her surgically-reduced assets in a white sheer puff-sleeved corseted ASOS top to attend the American Humane Hero Dog Awards in Los Angeles on Wednesday.</p>

<p>For the first time in months, the 22-year-old LA native hit the red carpet for the awards show airing October 19 on the Hallmark Channel.</p>

<p>Curiously, no one protected themselves or others from the coronavirus by wearing a mask or face covering, which California Governor Gavin Newsom made mandatory for public outings on June 18. </p>

