<p>In the COVID-19 era indie comedic thriller, Winter plays a woman who disappears during her virtual Zoom surprise birthday party, and her friends have to find her.</p>

<p>Ariel gushed of the film: 'This movie really is an ensemble and I'm honored to be sharing the screen with my friends, and producing this with a few of them as well!'</p>

<p>The aspiring federal prosecutor previously stated that she planned on resuming her studies at UCLA after dropping out in March 2018.</p>
